These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
Job: mechanic, nurse
Sport: skiing, water-polo
Game: poker, monopoly
1. Sport:skiing is on the right of Game:poker##1
2. Job:nurse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Job   | nurse    | mechanic |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Game     | poker     | monopoly      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
City: san-francisco, colone
Music-Genre: house, salsa
Transport: motorbike, train
1. Transport:train is on the left of City:san-francisco##1
2. Music-Genre:house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| City      | colone  | san-francisco   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | house  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

